{"tid":1802882,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[Cable] 修例風暴半年　港人經歷很多轉變","createTime":"2019-12-29T19:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T06:02:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"74ae8878601678c0a739d6d7d699a53e2b67bd20","tid":1802882,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:08:39.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞．走過2019】10月23日，陳同佳刑滿出獄，同日，保安局局長李家超在立法會宣布政府正式撤回《逃犯條例》草案。不過掀起的風暴已經遠遠超出修例，警民衝突愈演愈烈，市民對警隊的信心大跌。<br />\n<br />\n連月示威衝突使香港成為國際焦點，11月20日美國參眾兩院通過《香港人權及民主法案》，27日由美國總統特朗普簽署成法。<br />\n<br />\n這半年時間亦改變了區議會的政治版圖，民主派成為大贏家，不少當選人活躍於反修例運動，當中亦包括一些「政治素人」。<br />\n<br />\n到12月，林鄭月娥赴京述職，獲中央充分肯定，而走過2019，風暴未見平息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/14239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F14239&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK98ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=7e012ef3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F14239&h=1fad0a8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/14239</a>"},{"pid":"6d09ff891df476481cbead9cba43a6a9cec7377e","tid":1802882,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e128d4e754863a182e7e09acdcb1200f08273440","tid":1802882,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm